{"tid":302044,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"黑人演員唔得閒出席電影首映搵替身代勞 無人發現","createTime":"2017-06-29T05:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T16:42:31.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae234ccb1896b92339dc3ebd4c561dd0976abed2","tid":302044,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:38:21.000Z","msg":"Actor and comedian Hannibal Buress appears to have sent an imposter he recruited on social media to attend the Hollywood premiere of&nbsp;Spider-Man: Homecoming&nbsp;in his stead.<br />\n<br />\nBuress, who plays Coach Wilson in the superhero movie, tweeted Wednesday afternoon that he needed&nbsp;&ldquo;a lookalike with solid comedic timing for an event tonight.&rdquo; In the tweets, which have since been deleted, he also asked for photos and offered a $500 reward.<br />\n<br />\nHours later at the premiere &mdash; which was&nbsp;live-streamed on YouTube&nbsp;&mdash; a man identified as Hannibal Buress walked the red carpet and spoke about his role in&nbsp;Homecoming. The only problem is, he was not Hannibal Buress, as is clear from a screenshot that Buress sarcastically tweeted.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRepresentatives for Sony Pictures and Buress did not immediately respond to EW&rsquo;s request for comment about Buress&rsquo; stunt; reps for Marvel Studios declined to comment.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a1ob07qy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa1ob07qy&h=9000ff95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真身<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4d6klsft\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4d6klsft&h=577c770f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n替身<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔似喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820bc58738e3304ae3e705ed3318991d4d22bc91","tid":302044,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:40:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ew.com/movies/